"'''A ''Star Wars'' CELibration'''" is an article by [[Jon Bradley Snyder]] that appeared in [[Star Wars Insider 27|''Star Wars Insider'' 27]]. The article discusses [[Nelvana]]'s [[Star Wars: Droids: The Adventures of R2-D2 and C-3PO|''Droids'']] and [[Ewoks (television series)|''Ewoks'']] animated series and includes quotes from an interview with [[Clive Smith]], a co-founder of Nelvana.

The article also includes a '''Droids/Ewoks Episode Guide''' which gives short, informal summaries of each animated episode.

